latestPosts.caption:
i genuinely believe that people were put on this earth to just love one another. there are so many things we chase in life, but at the end of the day, this is truly the main purpose. to love hard, to care, and to live life with the people closest to us. this is what matters, and this is the only thing that’ll matter when we look back at life. love heals, love builds, and there is so much of it in this world. 

born to love- an idea so close to my heart- cuz this is really what we’re here for. 

hope u love it 

lots of love,
riya 🥰
